result.title: NOIP Will Start Soon
result.content: NOIP(National Olympiad in Informatics in Provinces) will start in October. Its difficulty is equal to problem A,B,C or B,B,C in Div.1. It's very difficult to me. So I must solve many problems whose difficulty is equal to problem A or B in Div.1. That's a big challenge to me. It'll cost me lots of time.
